Release v0.33 at 2017-08-29 — [learn more](https://github.com/wekan/wekan/blob/devel/CHANGELOG.md#v033-2017-08-29-wekan-release).

wekan-0.33.tar.gz is built on Ubuntu 14.04 64bit.

Wekan is available at official Sandstorm App Market.

Known bugs:

- On Sandstorm, Trello import does not import images, because on Wekan does not have Sandstorm-compatible network access to outside Sandstorm yet. So instad: Import from Trello to Standalone Wekan => Export to JSON => Import to Sandstorm.
- [Fix importing the activities minus attachments related activities](https://github.com/wekan/wekan/pull/1187) is not merged yet, and has attachment related activities missing.

[Docker Hub tag v0.33](https://hub.docker.com/r/wekanteam/wekan/tags/)

[Ubuntu snap](https://github.com/wekan/wekan-snap/wiki/Install)

FIXES  [SECURITY ISSUE: FILES ACCESSIBLE WITHOUT AUTHENTICATION](https://github.com/wekan/wekan/issues/1105).
